{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Forward.html#Lean.Elab.Do.tryElabForwardApp?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryElabForwardApp?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">dec</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Elaborate `e` as an application whose last argument is a `do←` body, performing the effect\nforwarding. Returns `none` if `e` doesn't have that shape.\n\nStrategy: build `headApp ?forwarded` with a fresh metavariable in the body slot and elaborate\nit. Lean's elaborator handles named args, defaults, and dot notation. We then check the\nwrapper's shape against the probe; on success, the lifted body is assigned into `?forwarded`\nand the probe expression itself is the result.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Forward.html#Lean.Elab.Do.tryElabForwardApp?","kind":"def","line":64,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.tryElabForwardApp?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Forward.lean#L64-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Forward.html#Lean.Elab.Do.elabDoForward\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabDoForward</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Term/TermElabM.html#Lean.Elab.Term.TermElab\">Term.TermElab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Forward.html#Lean.Elab.Do.elabDoForward","kind":"def","line":20,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.elabDoForward","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/BuiltinDo/Forward.lean#L20-L24"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Binders","Lean.Elab.Do.Basic","Lean.Elab.Do.Control","Lean.Elab.Do.InferControlInfo","Lean.Parser.Do"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.BuiltinDo.Forward"}